{"tid":1486132,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"部份路段交通燈號未能正常運作","createTime":"2019-08-18T18:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T19:30:18.000Z","uid":47555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c30025d643e22cf9ef0a25b94e83edaad7fd2c36","tid":1486132,"uid":47555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:45:24.000Z","msg":"其他消息<br />\n部份路段交通燈號未能正常運作<br />\n19/08/2019 02:34<br />\n<br />\n以下路段有交通燈號未能正常運作:<br />\n-英皇道與興發街交界<br />\n-軒尼詩道與菲林明道交界<br />\n-軒尼詩道(東行)與分域街交界<br />\n-軒尼詩道(東行)右轉波斯富街<br />\n<br />\n行人在交通燈號未能正常運作的路口橫過馬路時，請特別注意車輛。<br />\n駕駛人士駛經交界路口時，需小心駕駛，留意路口情況。<br />\n駕駛人士請盡量忍讓。市民請留意電台/電視廣播的最新交通情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5459bd22274d3bf1cf2445e3c59c9204cf3a07e5","tid":1486132,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:47:52.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借個位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要說「推」，試著說「８２３人鏈」<br />\n<br />\n８２３人鏈：香港之路Hong Kong Way正！式！上！線！！！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486119</a>"},{"pid":"d631298aba7598347b9b9b34410171663e52538e","tid":1486132,"uid":47555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}